export const toKebabCase = (str) =>
    str && str
      .match(/[A-Z]{2,}(?=[A-Z][a-z]+[0-9]*|\b)|[A-Z]?[a-z]+[0-9]*|[A-Z]{2,}|[0-9]+/g)
      .map((x) => x.toLowerCase())
      .join('-');
